<h2>What is TGHarker Identity?</h2>
<p>
    TGHarker Identity is a modern identity and access management platform built on OAuth 2.0 and OpenID Connect standards.
    It provides secure authentication, multi-tenant support, and comprehensive user management for your applications.
</p>

