<h2>OpenID Connect Discovery</h2>
<p>
    TGHarker Identity exposes standard OpenID Connect discovery endpoints. You can find the configuration at:
</p>

<pre><code>GET /.well-known/openid-configuration</code></pre>

<p>
    This endpoint returns all the information needed to configure your OAuth client, including:
</p>

<ul>
    <li>Authorization endpoint</li>
    <li>Token endpoint</li>
    <li>UserInfo endpoint</li>
    <li>Supported scopes and grant types</li>
    <li>JWKS URI for token validation</li>
</ul>
